These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, lacrosse, biathlon
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, spy, superhero
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, pall-mall, tiparillo
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, car, motorbike
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
2. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | baseball   | biathlon   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | disaster | superhero |
| Cigar   | tiparillo  | swisher    | pall-mall      |
| Transport     | car     | bus      | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, tea
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, dahlia
3 different pets are kept: frog, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person eating kale is the person who growspoppy##1
5. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking milk and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| Beverage   | milk     | tea     | cola      |
| Flower   | dahlia  | poppy | azalea |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | frog     | goat       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, skiing
House: victorian, gothic-revival, art-deco
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, thriller
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the victorian house is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the art-deco house and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Sport          | cricket  | skiing     | volleyball     |
| House           | art-deco | victorian  | gothic-revival   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | mystery    | thriller |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
3 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, mah-jongg
There are 3 different favourite colors: mauve, yellow, lavender
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the person playing monopoly and the person who likes mauve##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| Game     | monopoly    | mah-jongg  | bridge |
| Color     | yellow   | lavender | mauve        |
| Sport   | snowboarding | rowing     | rugby      |

