.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-5::.
There 3 different types of food: carrot, cherry, plum
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, satire, martial-arts
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, funk, gospel
House: victorian, palace, art-deco
1. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the victorian house is between the fan of gospel and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching horror movies is the palace house##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the victorian house is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Food          | plum    | carrot     | cherry      |
| Movie-Genre         | horror | satire | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | funk       | disco       |
| House           | palace     | victorian       | art-deco     |

