.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-6::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pumpkin
3 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, backgammon
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, country, d&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, daisy
1. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is the person playing billiard##1
3. the fan of country is between the person eating pineapple and the person who growsazalea##2
4. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Food          | pineapple | cauliflower | pumpkin    |
| Game         | monopoly | backgammon      | billiard |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | country     | d&b        |
| Flower           | bellflower      | daisy       | azalea      |

