.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, black, lavender
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indonesian, australian
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, roller, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the right of the egyptian##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who likes lavender and the person driving the car##2
3. the indonesian is on the right of the person who likes black##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the egyptian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Color          | lavender      | black   | ivory |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | australian | indonesian   |
| Transport     | van         | roller  | car       |

