.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
3 different games are played: whist, snooker, billiard
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, rock-climbing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, orchid, tulip
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, rock
1. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person playing billiard##2
5. the person playing snooker is the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Game      | whist       | snooker      | billiard      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | rock-climbing | chess      |
| Flower           | tulip | balloon-flower     | orchid |
| Music-Genre   | gospel     | rock          | folk       |

