3. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
4. the person eating papaya is on the far left##1
5. the indian is on the left of the victorian house##1
6. the victorian house is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |    3     |
| Game      | snooker      | go | domino     |
| Food          | papaya   | carrot      | peas     |
| Nationality   | russian  | indian      | nigerian |
| House     | craftsman | cottage        | victorian     |

