.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, milk
3 different pets are kept: pony, bird, guinea-pig
House: victorian, futuristic, cape-cod
There are 3 different nationalities: american, indonesian, italian
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the futuristic house##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the italian##1
3. the indonesian is in the middle##1
4. the indonesian is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the pony##2
5. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | milk     | hot-chocolate | coffee      |
| Pet         | bird  | guinea-pig       | pony |
| House   | cape-cod   | futuristic         | victorian     |
| Nationality   | american | indonesian    | italian     |

