.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea, tea
There 3 different types of food: potato, grapes, garlic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, musical, sports
City: colone, hannover, rome
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating garlic##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person eating grapes and the person watching musical movies##2
6. the person watching horror movies is the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Food           | potato | garlic | grapes |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | sports        | horror         |
| City   | hannover  | colone    | rome        |

