3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, pall-mall, davidoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the pilot is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the nurse is between the person playing backgammon and the owner of the snake##2
4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
