.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-14::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, red, chestnut
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, april, june
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, disaster, time-travel
1. the person who likes chestnut is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who's birthday is in june##2
2. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching disaster movies##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Color      | red    | chestnut          | coral |
| Birthday          | june | april           | august        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | time-travel    | disaster      |

