.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-15::.
City: venice, new-york, prague
3 different games are played: poker, billiard, go
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, nigerian, spanish
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, subway, train
1. the person playing go is on the left of the nigerian##1
2. the person driving the subway is between the person playing go and the spanish##2
3. the person driving the bike is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is between the person playing go and the person traveling to venice##2
5. the person playing billiard is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| City          | prague  | new-york   | venice |
| Game   | go  | billiard     | poker |
| Nationality   | chinese | nigerian | spanish   |
| Transport     | train   | subway   | bike      |

