.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-16::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, cain
3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, rat
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, lemonade
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, tram
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the horse##2
3. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person driving the boat##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Cigar       | cain | bolivar | alhambra |
| Pet         | horse   | rat       | mouse        |
| Beverage       | lemonade | sprite   | cola         |
| Transport   | tram    | train     | boat         |

