.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
House: futuristic, farmhouse, modern
3 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, pony
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, writer, scientist
1. the farmhouse house is between the scientist and the futuristic house##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the fan of electronic is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the pony is the fan of disco##1
5. the nurse is the owner of the hamster##1
6. the futuristic house is on the right of the writer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| House   | modern    | farmhouse | futuristic |
| Pet           | dog        | pony   | hamster  |
| Job     | scientist      | writer   | nurse |

