3. the indonesian is the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the lawyer is on the left of the turkish##1
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the writer is between the engineer and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |
