.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda
City: venice, san-francisco, nizza
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, sports, mystery
1. the person watching sports movies is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the fan of disco is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person traveling to venice##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking milk and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda     | milk        |
| City         | san-francisco   | nizza | venice |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery           | action    | sports       |

