.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, tulip
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, surfing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, fanta
1. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who growstulip##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Flower        | sunflower      | orchid | tulip |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Sport       | snowboarding | surfing   | lacrosse   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate          | milk     | fanta       |

 